        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">An ad blocker it is then.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Secondly, I would need to make a bot in order to do all the steps Iâ€™ve described in the fluxogram, without having to actually play those games (I may be good at Math, but Iâ€™m not <strong>that fast</strong>; and also, I wanted to make sure I got those 4 coins <strong>every time</strong>).</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-7">Blokada</h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Fortunately this app didnâ€™t have an ad-blocker detector. So I could use a tool like <a href="https://blokada.org/" target="_self">Blokada</a> to block all incoming ads and play games over and overâ€¦ without having to watch a single ad. In a nutshell, this app works like a <a href="https://www.kaspersky.com/resource-center/definitions/what-is-a-vpn" target="_self">VPN</a>, which makes it so, every time a request leaves the app:</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ul><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">It first goes to a Blokada server;</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">And then, if itâ€™s <strong>not</strong> an ad, it allows it to passthrough to where it was headed. If it isâ€¦ <em>â€œWhere do you think your going, ugh?â€</em></li></ul></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
